# supercronic crontab for the Grove synthetic Tier-1 runner.
# Every minute: run all journeys (shared health + per-tenant catalog/cart) and
# ship results to OpenObserve as OTLP metrics. supercronic logs each run to
# stdout and exits non-zero only on a scheduler fault (never on a journey
# failure — those are reported as metrics by run.py).
* * * * * python3 /app/run.py
